{
  "stem": "5371.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he told us, everybody has to be clean, has to wash himself, and he don't want anybody caught with dirty hands or dirty fingers or dirty feet or dirty ears or dirty head.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then they put us-- the next morning, they put us up in a room on the top of the building.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was like an attic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they taught us [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to be bricklayers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "First, they taught us about cement, about sand, about mixtures, about other things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Then they showed us how do lie the bricks down, to use a scale, to use the-- you know, when you put up-- when you run a wall, you put up a string, you know, like, stretch a string from one end to the wall to the other so you-- the bricks lay straight.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were there-- luckily, we were there for about two months.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was a very cold winter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were sitting there-- Now, the food was very minimal, no food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The bread was like sawdust, because we saw, at the end, that the-- like, sawdust-- actually sawdust.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we had a kapo there which was very, very nice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But we had his helpers, who were very bad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "In fact, they were Jewish guys from France.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "One was from France, was Maurice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And one was from Slovenia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they behaved very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were kicking also.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And for any little infraction, they beat you, they kicked you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And then in the-- in the-- every morning was roll call, and every evening was roll call.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They called your numbers, not your names.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And you had to answer to your number that you're there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] [SIGH] after two months they put us up on construction.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
